Package com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel

Contains the controller classes for accessing a controller and it's services.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IControllerStateListener
    State events of the controller.
    IControllerStateMonitor
    Interface used by controllers to report their status during initialization and while running.
    IControllerStateTracker
    Interface for components interested in the status of a controller.
    IFieldBusEventListener
    Interface for events based on the field bus.
    IStateTracker
    Interface for components interested in the status of a group of controllers.
    ITrackerRegistry
    Enables registration of controller state trackers to a registry.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ControllerParameterSet
    Represents a set of parameters.
    ControllerStateInfo
    Contains information about a controller.
    DispatchedEventData
    Details about an event that occurred in the system.
    DispatchedEventLogRecord
    Specific Sunrise log record that contains information about event changes.
    StatePortData
    Details about the state ports.
    StatePortData.PropertyState
    Details about the state of an state port.
    StatePortLogRecord
    Specific Sunrise log record that contains information about state port changes.
    VersionInfoData
    VersionInfoData contains version information for multiple slaves.
